  "stem": "<p>The graph below models the number of active subscriptions, in thousands, that a service had <i>x</i> months after the end of May 2018, for 0 &le; <i>x</i> &le; 8. Based on the graph, after how many months did the service reach its greatest number of active subscriptions?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><figure class='image'><svg role=\"img\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 360 320\" width=\"360\" height=\"320\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"Graph of a downward-opening parabola with vertex at (4, 12) passing through (0, 4) and (8, 4).\"><defs><style>.ax{stroke:#333;stroke-width:1.2;fill:none}.gr{stroke:#ddd;stroke-width:0.6;fill:none}.cv{stroke:#1f77b4;stroke-width:2;fill:none}.pt{fill:#1f77b4}.lb{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;fill:#222}</style></defs><rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"360\" height=\"320\" fill=\"#fff\"/><g class=\"gr\"><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"85\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"120\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"120\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"155\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"155\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"190\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"225\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"225\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"260\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"295\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"295\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"330\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"40\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"80\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"120\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"160\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"160\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"200\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"240\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"240\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"280\"/></g><g class=\"ax\"><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"340\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"280\"/></g><path class=\"cv\" d=\"M 50 240 Q 190 -40 330 240\"/><circle class=\"pt\" cx=\"190\" cy=\"40\" r=\"3.5\"/><circle class=\"pt\" cx=\"50\" cy=\"240\" r=\"3.5\"/><circle class=\"pt\" cx=\"330\" cy