  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. The greatest number of active subscriptions corresponds to the maximum value of the function, which occurs at the vertex of the downward-opening parabola. From the graph, the vertex is at (4, 12), so the maximum occurs at <i>x</i> = 4 months.</p><p>Choice B is the right endpoint of the domain, not the vertex. Choice C is the <i>y</i>-coordinate of the vertex (peak value), not the time. Choice D is unrelated to the labeled vertex.</p>",
